### Welcome opendata-models Pages.
This is an automaticly generated page some #opendata related models and conceptualizations. These pagea are in in the original repo as branc gh-pages and can be found like this:
```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch
